Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.03,0:00:07.94,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,You came after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.94,0:00:09.11,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Amber...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.82,0:00:11.41,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Thanks, Yin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.90,0:00:14.16,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Everyone died, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.65,0:00:22.48,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Sorry, I don't have much time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.01,0:00:30.30,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,There's no doubt that something's going on in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:34.30,DTB-Default,Kouno,0,0,0,,What are we supposed to do? It would be pretty pathetic to launch a two-man attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.05,0:00:40.11,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,It's Ohtsuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.11,0:00:40.77,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:44.42,DTB-Default,Mayu,0,0,0,,What kind of question is that? There's nobody from the division here, and...
