Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.05,0:00:50.34,DTB-Default,Mayu,0,0,0,,To be honest, I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.34,0:00:54.13,DTB-Default,Mayu,0,0,0,,The solar maximum will enter its final stage soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.53,0:00:57.60,DTB-Default,Mayu,0,0,0,,Will Tokyo continue to...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.45,0:01:25.00,DTB-Default,Kouno,0,0,0,,This is insane! It's practically a war!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.10,0:01:28.40,DTB-Default,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.97,0:01:33.15,DTB-Default,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,Hurry up! If we're going to force our way in, we have to do it while they're distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.74,0:01:39.73,DTB-Default,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,You understand what this means, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.73,0:01:42.02,DTB-Default,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,We're up against more than contractors.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.97,0:01:47.22,DTB-Default,Guard,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.22,0:01:55.11,DTB-Default,Operator A,0,0,0,,We're now approaching the maximum activity period of the solar maximum, its final stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.56,0:01:57.86,DTB-Default,Operator A,0,0,0,,Maximum level of the Gullfinger wave acknowledged.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.28,0:02:02.10,DTB-Default,Operator B,0,0,0,,The anti-gate particle generation level within the accelerator ring is at maximum.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:07.31,DTB-Default,Schroeder,0,0,0,,Collect all the energy from the Saturn Ring and direct it to {\i1}Hope{\i0}, the auxiliary convergency unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.31,0:02:09.03,DTB-Default,Schroeder,0,0,0,,This is a race, people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.03,0:02:11.93,DTB-Default,Schroeder,0,0,0,,A race between the E.P.R. and human beings. There can only be one victor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.93,0:02:14.88,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,Activate all internal surveillance cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.88,0:02:17.03,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,Locate BK201 at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:23.09,DTB-Default,Schroeder,0,0,0,,Not even BK201 will be able to reach the core without the aid of a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.09,0:02:24.29,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,It's merely a precautionary measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.67,0:02:30.02,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,I thought a large hole would have formed here,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.02,0:02:33.36,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,but there isn't anything at all. What a desolate place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.89,0:02:36.71,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,We can't move in any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.18,0:02:38.66,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,This is good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:42.72,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,We couldn't even get this close in South America.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.12,0:02:45.77,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like they're angry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.00,0:02:49.73,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,It's probably because of that kitty cat and that child.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.76,0:02:52.41,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,They relayed the information well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:58.77,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,I wasn't interested in the purpose of your resistance until I arrived here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.25,0:03:00.62,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Did you have a change of heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:04.68,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Have you been doing this since South America?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:08.50,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Were you fighting against the syndicate since that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:12.67,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,We didn't have as many members back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:16.28,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Besides, we didn't even realize their intentions until much later,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:19.97,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,after we fought Heaven's War several times.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.69,0:03:26.74,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Many more stars fell back then compared to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.17,0:03:32.66,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Why we were ordered to continue spying, why we were ordered to kill,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.66,0:03:34.93,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,it never crossed our minds at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.93,0:03:39.40,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,We blindly followed the orders we were given.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:42.74,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,We're contractors. All we had to do was act rationally.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.85,0:03:46.13,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,One day, things started to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.92,0:03:50.66,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,It wasn't a result of somebody taking the initiative. It just happened gradually.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.62,0:03:55.93,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,We were referring to each other as partners before we even realized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:58.40,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,We started sharing information.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.06,0:04:01.49,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Your sister was one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.49,0:04:02.63,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Pai?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.14,0:04:06.26,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,She was the one who initially discovered the syndicate's plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:09.44,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,I'm not surprised you didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.44,0:04:13.98,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,She didn't want to drag you, of all people, into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.22,0:04:23.40,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Unlike us, you've always been a human being, Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:28.92,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it have been difficult to choose between the life of a human and a contractor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.69,0:04:31.15,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,That's why she...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:33.47,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Since when?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.35,0:04:35.68,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Since when did Pai...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:37.72,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:39.25,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Little by little,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:43.29,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,she began to accept the fact that she had become a contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.29,0:04:46.25,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Every time you followed the syndicate's orders,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:48.80,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,she gradually became more sad and hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:51.67,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,That eventually led to a change within her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:56.18,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Why would I know about her feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.18,0:04:59.98,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,It's because I felt the same way. That child does, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.85,0:05:03.68,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,They may not have realized it yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.68,0:05:08.05,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,but they are gradually changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.51,0:05:13.63,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,I don't know who created this gate or why they did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.63,0:05:19.23,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,All I know is that the contract we signed simply represented the beginning of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:26.25,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,The beginning of something that might happen a hundred, ten thousand, or a hundred thousand years from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:28.97,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:30.78,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Why did you hide it from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.80,0:05:35.43,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,You wouldn't have believed me unless I told you under these circumstances, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:40.30,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,You would have tried to escape the syndicate if I said anything, Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.88,0:05:43.92,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,If that happened, you wouldn't be alive today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.88,0:05:47.69,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,It's coming soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.69,0:05:48.61,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,It?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:52.33,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,The arrival of the existence that will completely erase contractors and the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.96,0:05:55.89,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,It's what we want to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:05:59.39,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Hei,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:03.21,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,do you want to see Pai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.46,0:06:13.14,DTB-Default,Operator A,0,0,0,,The convergence beam unit is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.14,0:06:17.85,DTB-Default,Operator A,0,0,0,,Executing final adjustments for core emission of anti-gate particles.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:19.53,DTB-Default,Operator B,0,0,0,,Presence of a chain reaction confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.53,0:06:21.90,DTB-Default,Operator B,0,0,0,,One hundred and eighty seconds until emission.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:24.73,DTB-Default,Operator B,0,0,0,,The Saturn System is about to enter its final stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:27.83,DTB-Default,Schroeder,0,0,0,,At last, after all that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.82,0:06:38.04,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Isn't it strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:41.90,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,I broke it and gave a piece to everyone before I came here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:44.04,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,but it reverted back to its original shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:46.13,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,What are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:48.51,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,I'm going to do the same thing I did in South America.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:51.80,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,I'm going to release Pai's powers before it arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:55.24,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,When I do, no one will be able to approach this area,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:57.22,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,just like Heaven's Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:07:00.23,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Go ahead, Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:03.74,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,What are you asking me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.74,0:07:07.08,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Come on. You should have realized it by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.08,0:07:09.32,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Pai has always been within you, Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.84,0:07:14.26,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,She's been with you ever since the day you thought she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.94,0:07:19.86,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,The ability to conduct electricity was only one of Pai's abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.86,0:07:23.75,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,You should know the source of your powers better than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:27.67,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Come on, Hei. Let's go meet Pai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.46,0:07:30.06,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,What will become of this city?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:36.13,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,If I use my powers for the sake of meeting Pai,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.13,0:07:40.77,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,what will become of the contractors, humans... everyone who lives here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:43.23,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Will they disappear like they did in South America?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:48.15,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:51.26,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Contractors as a whole will disappear if you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:56.32,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Yin, me... Every single contractor on this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.89,0:08:00.48,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Everyone except you, Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:06.33,DTB-Default,Operator A,0,0,0,,Convergent energy will soon reach critical levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.33,0:08:07.97,DTB-Default,Operator B,0,0,0,,Core point at hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.97,0:08:10.94,DTB-Default,Operator B,0,0,0,,Focus and tolerance revisions for the lens are complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:13.01,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,Begin the countdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:16.80,DTB-Default,Schroeder,0,0,0,,Wait a second! Let me do the honors!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:19.39,DTB-Default,Schroeder,0,0,0,,This is a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity. Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:23.40,DTB-Default,Schroeder,0,0,0,,{\an8}20, 19, 18, 17,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:22.89,DTB-Default,Operator A,0,0,0,,We have a live feed of the core area.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.40,0:08:26.91,DTB-Default,Schroeder,0,0,0,,{\an8}16, 15, 14,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.53,0:08:26.91,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,Did they back off?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.91,0:08:28.61,DTB-Default,Schroeder,0,0,0,,{\an8}13, 12,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:28.61,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:31.39,DTB-Default,Schroeder,0,0,0,,{\an8}11, 10, 9,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:32.94,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,BK201 won't cause the explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:34.41,DTB-Default,Schroeder,0,0,0,,{\an8}8, 7, 6,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.94,0:08:34.41,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,He's not sure about what he's doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:36.37,DTB-Default,Schroeder,0,0,0,,{\an8}5, 4,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:36.37,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:39.55,DTB-Default,Schroeder,0,0,0,,3, 2, 1,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:44.92,DTB-Default,Schroeder,0,0,0,,0!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.73,0:09:58.17,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,No... No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.07,0:10:01.64,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,I never wanted to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.15,0:10:04.75,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,I didn't want everything to disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.74,0:10:07.71,DTB-Default,Bai,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.45,0:10:09.50,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:10.75,DTB-Default,Bai,0,0,0,,You're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:12.38,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:13.46,DTB-Default,Bai,0,0,0,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:15.01,DTB-Default,Bai,0,0,0,,I said I wasn't lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:17.93,DTB-Default,Bai,0,0,0,,Why are you crying, Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:22.87,DTB-Default,Bai,0,0,0,,I had known all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:26.96,DTB-Default,Bai,0,0,0,,I knew you never wanted to kill anyone, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.72,0:10:30.90,DTB-Default,Bai,0,0,0,,In order to accept me as a contractor,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:34.14,DTB-Default,Bai,0,0,0,,you've been doing things against your will, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.14,0:10:37.35,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Wrong. I'm the Grim Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.35,0:10:38.84,DTB-Default,Bai,0,0,0,,No, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.77,0:10:42.80,DTB-Default,Bai,0,0,0,,You're my brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:47.16,DTB-Default,Bai,0,0,0,,so don't push yourself too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.60,0:10:50.94,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Geez, you're always screwing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:52.95,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Don't bite off more than you can chew!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:53.53,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Huang?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.53,0:10:59.14,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Do you realize how many times you've pissed me off because of your indecisive nature?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.14,0:11:02.44,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,That's what makes Hei so interesting, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.44,0:11:03.25,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Mao?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.25,0:11:07.89,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Who would have thought you'd be uncertain about your own identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:12.18,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,No wonder you didn't act like a contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.18,0:11:18.53,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Got it? You're human. You're only making things more complicated by masquerading as a contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.78,0:11:23.20,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,If you can't choose between the two, choose both!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:26.70,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,A decision befitting a human being and a contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:28.22,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:42.72,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Is that really okay with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.17,0:11:46.35,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Is that your answer, Hei?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.94,0:11:51.10,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,By choosing to assume both identities, you'll only make life more difficult on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:55.31,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,The syndicate will do whatever it takes to capture you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:59.82,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,You'll have to kill again if you choose to walk that path.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:02.07,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Didn't you tell me you were sick of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:06.07,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,You're only going to lose everything you've managed to gain again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:10.29,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,You won't be able to see the real stars or your beloved sister anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:11.22,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Will you still...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.09,0:12:15.34,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.27,0:12:19.74,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,Isn't this what you've always wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:21.32,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,That's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:25.09,DTB-Default,November,0,0,0,,Aren't you the one who's afraid of letting him choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:31.70,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Amber, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.35,0:12:38.74,DTB-Default,Amber,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear another word.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.02,0:12:47.41,DTB-Default,Bai,0,0,0,,Good-bye, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:50.91,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Good-bye, Qing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:53.91,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Good-bye, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:56.92,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Good-bye, Amber.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.58,0:13:15.11,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:17.77,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:19.33,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Yin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:22.01,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Hei, come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.01,0:13:22.84,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Yin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:25.57,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Don't leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.18,0:13:35.98,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.47,0:13:37.04,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:41.80,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Where's Amber?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.17,0:13:48.56,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,She used her ability one last time,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.03,0:13:51.68,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,which is what she planned on doing from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.97,0:13:56.06,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.57,0:13:59.79,DTB-Default,Operator A,0,0,0,,Convergent energy will soon reach critical levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.79,0:14:01.44,DTB-Default,Operator B,0,0,0,,Core point at hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:04.40,DTB-Default,Operator B,0,0,0,,Focus and tolerance revisions for the lens are complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.93,0:14:06.40,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,Begin the countdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:10.21,DTB-Default,Schroeder,0,0,0,,Wait a second! Let me do the honors!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.21,0:14:12.49,DTB-Default,Schroeder,0,0,0,,This is a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity. Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:16.16,DTB-Default,Schroeder,0,0,0,,{\an8}20, 19, 18, 17,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:16.16,DTB-Default,Operator A,0,0,0,,We have a live feed of the core area.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.16,0:14:19.61,DTB-Default,Schroeder,0,0,0,,{\an8}16, 15, 14,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:19.18,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,Did they back off?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.61,0:14:21.75,DTB-Default,Schroeder,0,0,0,,{\an8}13, 12,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:21.45,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:24.52,DTB-Default,Schroeder,0,0,0,,{\an8}11, 10, 9,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.03,0:14:24.40,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,BK201 isn't at the core!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:25.76,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,There won't be an explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.52,0:14:27.59,DTB-Default,Schroeder,0,0,0,,{\an8}8, 7, 6,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:27.59,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,The threat has been eliminated!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.59,0:14:29.68,DTB-Default,Schroeder,0,0,0,,{\an8}5, 4,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:29.68,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:32.60,DTB-Default,Schroeder,0,0,0,,3, 2, 1,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:33.85,DTB-Default,Schroeder,0,0,0,,0!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:41.09,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.09,0:14:42.13,DTB-Default,Operator,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:45.72,DTB-Default,Operator,0,0,0,,A Lancer Black reaction has been detected within the Saturn Ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:47.32,DTB-Default,Operator,0,0,0,,It's growing by the second!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.14,0:14:49.30,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,Find out what's causing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.94,0:14:56.79,DTB-Default,Schroeder,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:08.63,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,BK201!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.08,0:15:11.55,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,Take him down! Shoot him now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.61,0:15:25.12,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,Prepare for the second emission immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.89,0:15:26.97,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.97,0:15:28.56,DTB-Default,Schroeder,0,0,0,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.56,0:15:30.66,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,Useless? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.66,0:15:35.01,DTB-Default,Schroeder,0,0,0,,The anti-gate particles within the system have been completely altered
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.01,0:15:39.87,DTB-Default,Schroeder,0,0,0,,by the special particle light emitted from BK201's electric current.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:43.46,DTB-Default,Schroeder,0,0,0,,His electric current isn't one made up of mere electromagnetic waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:47.26,DTB-Default,Schroeder,0,0,0,,It's capable of altering substances at a quantum level.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:52.51,DTB-Default,Schroeder,0,0,0,,Granting the abilities of a contractor to an ordinary human being is an example of what BK201 is capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:55.35,DTB-Default,Schroeder,0,0,0,,I thought the same incident that took place in South America would happen again,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:16:01.51,DTB-Default,Schroeder,0,0,0,,where the altered substance would saturate the gate and create a neutral territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.51,0:16:05.96,DTB-Default,Schroeder,0,0,0,,Who would have thought he'd attack the Saturn Ring with pinpoint accuracy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:08.46,DTB-Default,Schroeder,0,0,0,,He really outdid us this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:12.11,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,Somebody take this man away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.14,0:16:14.07,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.51,0:16:17.16,DTB-Default,Nishijima,0,0,0,,How could the syndicate terminate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.23,0:16:33.09,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,We've been conducting undercover investigations on a suspect, namely Eric Nishijima,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:36.65,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,on charges of conspiracy and violation of United Nation laws.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:39.85,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,The perfect scapegoat, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:45.42,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Is this your... the syndicate's method of handling things?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:48.61,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,I need not remind you about how Intelligence is supposed to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:59.03,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Manager Hourai, you and Eric Nishijima, who you just killed, attempted to eliminate all contractors
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:17:02.62,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,despite the fact that the threat of an explosion didn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.52,0:17:08.63,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Weren't you the ones who instigated all this, not the E.P.R.,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.33,0:17:11.83,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,in an effort to eradicate them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.83,0:17:13.26,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,Do you have any evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.99,0:17:20.71,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Eventually, the time will come when the truth is disclosed. History will be the judge of your actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.71,0:17:24.85,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Don't think you can get away with it at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:27.73,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,The existence of the syndicate or the relationship I maintained with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:30.86,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,you can't prove either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:33.75,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,You have no idea how influential the syndicate is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.75,0:17:36.34,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,However, due to this disturbance,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.34,0:17:40.20,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,knowledge about the existence of contractors will inevitably become known to the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:44.54,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,We should have eliminated information about them before it came to that,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:48.52,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,while they were still a nameless cluster of stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.05,0:17:50.55,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,That will be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.02,0:17:52.30,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,Enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.94,0:17:57.05,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I've recorded this conversation. Please come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.11,0:18:02.70,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,So you opted for a third route, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:07.00,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,Why don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:11.16,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,The path you've chosen is one of massive conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:14.50,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,The human race will abhor contractors all the more,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.50,0:18:16.58,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,and contractors will act in kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.58,0:18:18.80,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,What do you think will be the end result of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.37,0:18:22.71,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,You advocate peace,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.71,0:18:25.16,DTB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,so there isn't any reason why you shouldn't understand what I'm trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.39,0:18:40.89,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.72,0:18:45.87,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.53,0:18:48.24,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Wait, Li-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:52.23,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,The man you once knew as Li no longer exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.34,0:19:02.49,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:03.53,DTB-Default,Kouno,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.53,0:19:04.49,DTB-Default,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.49,0:19:05.59,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.59,0:19:08.02,DTB-Default,Kouno,0,0,0,,This is awful. What the hell happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:08.88,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,Manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.88,0:19:11.04,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Saitou, arrest the manager
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.82,0:19:13.61,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,on charges of homicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:16.00,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:18.61,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,He might try to commit suicide, so be alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.61,0:19:19.29,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:21.62,DTB-Default,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,In any case, let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.62,0:19:22.07,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:32.96,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Our lives returned to normal shortly after that incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.42,0:19:40.05,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,As the manager had predicted,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:44.28,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,contractor-related incidents were on the rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:49.00,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,Freeze! Slowly raise your hands and turn toward me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.78,0:20:01.72,DTB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,2048 hours, suspect detained.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:02.85,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.03,0:20:08.75,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,There wasn't a single trace of the syndicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:14.31,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,However, it was only a matter of time until the existence of contractors became known to the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.89,0:20:21.11,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,One day, in the near future, our moment of truth will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.80,0:20:27.71,DTB-Default,Hoshimi,0,0,0,,That's it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.71,0:20:30.49,DTB-Default,Hoshimi,0,0,0,,take them with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.92,0:20:33.57,DTB-Default,Hoshimi,0,0,0,,The stars that have fallen,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.57,0:20:36.10,DTB-Default,Hoshimi,0,0,0,,the stars that are falling,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.10,0:20:38.73,DTB-Default,Hoshimi,0,0,0,,every single one of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:42.35,DTB-Default,Hoshimi,0,0,0,,Yes. Far, far,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.35,0:20:49.56,DTB-Default,Hoshimi,0,0,0,,far, far away, to a future nobody has ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.37,0:20:52.94,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was really sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.94,0:20:56.75,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,Why would they deport such a nice man?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:21:00.96,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,There are so many Japanese who are much worse than he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.46,0:21:24.34,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Would we have chosen the same path,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.34,0:21:26.79,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,a path of coexistence?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.79,0:21:27.76,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.35,0:21:32.69,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I wanted to hear his answer with my own ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.08,0:21:44.78,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:48.29,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Understood. I'll be there soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.32,0:22:09.32,Title,,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(957,322)}Episode Twenty-Five
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.32,0:22:09.32,Title,,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(976,639)}Does the Reaper Dream of Darkness, \NDarker Than Black?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.27,0:22:16.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, hello there. Matsumoto, Public Security Bureau, Foreign Affairs Section 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.52,0:22:18.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure that this was the last episode,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.55,0:22:20.58,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,but actually, there appears to be one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.58,0:22:22.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Now, in the spring comes flower-viewing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:25.15,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The other day, even Section 4 went out to see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.15,0:22:27.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There, a young lady of ours, named Otsuka-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.62,0:22:29.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,started going on about what she liked. She says,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.85,0:22:35.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,"I prefer men, like you, Matsumoto-san, rather than younger men."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.12,0:22:37.78,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What was I saying? Oh yes, the preview.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.35,0:22:41.38,Title,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hf2f2f2&\fscx80}Episode Twenty-Six
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.35,0:22:41.38,Title,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hf2f2f2&\fscx80}Beneath Cherry Blossoms in Full Bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.78,0:22:40.44,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Time's up? Well, if you'll excuse me...